# Communication Specs

## Purpose

This directory contains generated communication contracts for structured loop messages.

## Contents

- `comms-overview.md`: generated overview of message families, routes, replies, and lifecycle effects when emitted.
- `templates.toml`: generated template registry when structured messages are emitted.
- `schemas/`: generated JSON Schemas for structured payloads.
- `renderers/`: generated human-readable Markdown render templates.
